\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/25/184440_cbaa681288a0395fcec89389afe15473.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F25%2F184440_cbaa681288a0395fcec89389afe15473.jpeg&h=5eab054f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/25/184442_e90c7c9bdfcac7ba03fc0829d3f5c14a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F25%2F184442_e90c7c9bdfcac7ba03fc0829d3f5c14a.jpeg&h=c9712cba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n重慶玩到咁<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171225/57624012\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171225%2F57624012&d=ZOOWPitwjGLyUMxvqtd0szQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=5f481cd9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171225%2F57624012&h=d63eda91\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171225/57624012</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n過多幾年香港都會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n班老野求仁得仁啦，共享中國人榮耀聖誕節都無撚得過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過到時佢地應該都獲毛澤東接見啦"},{"pid":"6a820d335dae599b3b6fa83779fe16b47ca3e527","tid":509452,"uid":37463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T14:05:14.000Z","msg":"問下民建聯果班耶撚<br />\n點睇棋王呢步棋<br />\n應唔應該跟主席抵制聖誕節？<br />\n<br />\n例子<br />\n蔣麗芸［民建聯］ - 天主教<br />\n梁美芬［經民聯］ - 基督教<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dc130329b1d858e81ebf9f0b51aef310ca72585","tid":509452,"uid":93217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T14:12:42.000Z","msg":"快啲鎖國啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df880de5540d1376e6fdf5460004d4e0e45fd20b","tid":509452,"uid":55879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T14:14:17.000Z","msg":"咁應該禁制埋班蝗落黎香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3a70943b18b82e5320768e23e80dc97f3b47889","tid":509452,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T14:15:19.000Z","msg":"【內地聖誕彌撒保安嚴密】【神職人員感恩領導感恩祖國】<br />\n<br />\n聖誕快樂！在內地，要過一個有氣氛的聖誕節不是難事，但若要一個富宗教氣氛的聖誕，則不是那麼容易了。<br />\n<br />\n在北京和廣州，當局都派駐了不少公安和特警在教堂外巡邏。在進入教堂前，信徒都要經過安檢，搜身、搜袋後才可順利通過。有教堂人員表示，全年只有這兩天才有如此嚴格的監管，平常都不用安檢和取票。<br />\n<br />\n就連神父在做彌撤時，都特別提及此安排，對祖國和執勤人員的付出表示感恩，「感謝在今天所有為我們平安夜到來付出的各級領導，各級領導所帶著的執勤人員，有可能比我們見到他們的人更多，再感謝我們的祖國，保證了今天這麼一個和平祥和的機會，所以謝謝他們。」<br />\n<br />\n#子夜彌撒<br />\n#平安夜崇拜<br />\n#保安嚴密<br />\n#神父感謝主感謝領導感謝祖國<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/1594538564023957/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2Fvideos%2F1594538564023957%2F&d=ZOOWPitwjGLyUMxvqtd0szQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=b88614ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/1594538564023957/</a>"},{"pid":"9f1acd2b7a4ee556520ee9a305c2257ca7d12276","tid":509452,"uid":18251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T14:19:19.000Z","msg":"好嘢文革再臨<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你咪又係靜靜雞出國興祝聖誕<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4df8d298ea99ac0e6b42b06a83c7fe02f465a6c4","tid":509452,"uid":19093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T14:36:02.000Z","msg":"唔好用西歷， 用返農歴，星期日唔好放假丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1abc4ce73d60739bfe1be3dd03b50ab2b098be25","tid":509452,"uid":34222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T14:38:35.000Z","msg":"雜種先係中國既神